cast.overview: The story of Gary Valentine and Alana Kane growing up, running around and going through the treacherous navigation of first love in the San Fernando Valley, 1973.
cast.title: Licorice Pizza

details.biography: Danielle Sari Haim (born February 16, 1989) is an American musician, singer and songwriter from Los Angeles, California, the daughter of Israeli footballer Mordechai Haim. She is the lead guitarist of the American pop rock band Haim, which also consists of her two sisters, Este Haim and Alana Haim. In 2021, she appeared in Paul Thomas Anderson's film Licorice Pizza alongside Cooper Hoffman and the rest of Haim.
details.name: Danielle Haim
